<div class="bg-warning bg-opacity-50 text-center py-2">
    <strong>First login: admin/admin</strong>
</div>

<div class="container">
    <h1 class="mt-5 mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <h2 class="blue-text">1. HR Manager</h2>
    <p>Upon opening the system, the HR Manager will see options to navigate to the following sections:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>List of Employees</li>
        <li>List of Projects</li>
        <li>List of Leave Requests</li>
        <li>List of Approval Requests</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>With a List of Employees, the HR Manager can:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><s>Sort table rows using sorting in the column headers.</s> <span class="text-danger text-opacity-50 mx-5">Added next week</span></li>
        <li><s>Search by name for table rows.</s> <span class="text-danger text-opacity-50 mx-5">Added next week</span></li>
        <li>Add, update, or deactivate employees in the list.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>With a List of Approval Requests, the HR Manager can:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><s>Sort table rows using sorting in the column headers.</s> <span class="text-danger text-opacity-50 mx-5">Added next week</span></li>
        <li><s>Search by request number for table rows.</s> <span class="text-danger text-opacity-50 mx-5">Added next week</span></li>
        <li>Open a request – a new form opens with details.</li>
        <li>Approve the request – the related leave request is updated with the corresponding status, and employee absence balance is recalculated.</li>
        <li><strong>Reject the request</strong> – the related leave request is updated with the corresponding status. <em>Note: Rejection functionality should be possible to ensure complete approval process management.</em></li>
    </ul>

    <h4>With a List of Leave Requests, the HR Manager can:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><s>Sort table rows using sorting in the column headers.</s> <span class="text-danger text-opacity-50 mx-5">Added next week</span></li>
        <li><s>Search by request number for table rows.</s> <span class="text-danger text-opacity-50 mx-5">Added next week</span></li>
        <li>Open a request – a new form opens with details.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>With a List of Projects, the HR Manager can:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><s>Sort table rows using sorting in the column headers.</s> <span class="text-danger text-opacity-50 mx-5">Added next week</span></li>
        <li><s>Use filters for table rows.</s> <span class="text-danger text-opacity-50 mx-5">Added next week</span></li>
        <li><s>Search by request number for table rows.</s> <span class="text-danger text-opacity-50 mx-5">Added next week</span></li>
        <li>Open a project – a new form opens with details.</li>
    </ul>

