    </ul>

    <h2 class="blue-text">3. Company Employees</h2>
    <p>Upon opening the system, employees will see options to navigate to the following sections:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>List of their projects</li>
        <li>List of leave requests</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>With a List of Leave Requests, employees can:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><s>Sort table rows using sorting in the column headers.</s> <span class="text-danger text-opacity-50 mx-5">Added next week</span></li>
        <li><s>Use filters for table rows.</s> <span class="text-danger text-opacity-50 mx-5">Added next week</span></li>
        <li><s>Search by request number for table rows.</s> <span class="text-danger text-opacity-50 mx-5">Added next week</span></li>
        <li>Open a new or existing request – a form opens where employees can create and update the request.</li>
        <li>Submit the request – the status is updated to “Submitted,” and a new approval request is created for the responsible HR Manager and Project Managers responsible for the employee’s projects.</li>
        <li>Cancel the request – the status is updated to “Canceled,” and any existing approval requests are canceled.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<title>System Roles</title>
<div class="container my-5">
    <h2 class="text-center mb-4 blue-text">Roles in the System</h2>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <table class="table table-bordered">
                <thead class="bg-opacity-25 bg-dark">
                    <tr>
                        <th>Role</th>
                        <th>Description of Main Tasks</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="bg-light">
                    <tr>
                        <td>Employee</td>
                        <td>Creates a leave request</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>HR Manager</td>
                        <td>Manages the list of employees<br>Approves/rejects requests</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Project Manager</td>
                        <td>Manages the list of projects<br>Approves/rejects requests</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Administrator</td>
                        <td>Grants access rights<br>Manages all data</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="container text-center mt-5 mb-5">
    <a class="display-6 text-decoration-none blue-text">DB Schema Overview</a>
</div>
<div class="mb-5 text-center">
    <img src="~/dbschema.svg" alt="Db Schema" class="d-block mx-auto p-3" style="max-width: 100%;" />
</div>


